<a id="top"/> <strong><em>TO ALL USERS</em>: If you are not a game developer or a moderator, please do not edit the content of this page, or its sub-pages. You may contribute via <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation#head-7fa0a174d9f0cdb4daff4e27c889516ddeb06a90"><img src="./wiki/classic/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">User suggestions</a>, where anyone is welcome to contribute a thread. Thank you!</strong> --- <strong><a href="./TheFalcon">TheFalcon</a></strong> 2005-03-15 16:58:35 <p>
This page is designed to provide an introduction and overview of the ToME magic system. 
</p>
